fr.ign.cogit.geoxygene.spatial.coordgeom

Class GM_Envelope

  • Object
    • GM_Envelope
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEnvelope

    public class GM_Envelope
extends Object
implements IEnvelope
    Rectangle englobant minimum en 2D, ou pave englobant minimium en 3D. Un GM_envelope est parallele aux axes.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Thierry Badard, Arnaud Braun
